quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  3,149,"Kon on yo gom…óim…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, si on …óoftike …ďen yeddu…ďe immorde e Alyahuuda e Annasaara e …ďen sirkoo…ďe ; e kon ko …ďe yamirta on e majjere, …ďe ruttay on …ďaawo gom…óinal mon e keeferaku mon aranu, woŇčton hayru…ďe aduna e laakara."
  3,150,"∆Āee heefer…ďe wallataa on si on …óoftike …ďe, si ko woni, ko Alla woni Walloowo on e ay…ďe mo'on, …óoftee Mo, ko KaŇčko woni Senii…óo …ďur…óo mo∆ī∆īude e walloo…ďe, o hatonjiŇčtaa e gooto …ďaawo Makko."
  3,151,"Arma Men Bugoo e …ďer…óe …ďen yeddu…ďe, kulol tii…óungol, haa tawa …ďe ha…ótanaaka tabitugol ka hare ; …óum non, ka sabu kafidugol ma…ď…ďe ngol Alla e rewetee…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin …ói Alla Jippinanaali …ďe e fii majji hujja. Jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe nden non ka laakara, ko ka yiite, nge bonii jaa∆īorde …ďen too√Īoo…ďe."
  3,152,"Gom…óii Alla Hunnanii on ko O Fodunoo on wallitagol on e ay…ďe mo'on √Īalnde uhud, tuma warayno…óon …ďe e DuŇčayee Alla, haa nde cooyna…óon lo'u…óon e tabitugol e ko Nulaa…óo on yamiri on e muu…óun; lurru…óon hakkunde heddagol e nokkeeli mon maa yahugol moo…ďa dammi; yeddu…óon Nulaa…óo on e ko o yamiri on heddagol ka nokkeeli mon no woniri woo. No e mon …ďen faalaa…ďe dammi aduna ; …ďe yahunoo fii majji, no e mon kadi …ďen faalaa…ďe mbarjaari laakara ; ko …ďen heddinoo ka yamiraa …óon …ďe …óoftii Nulaa…óo on. Refti non Alla Yiiliri on e ma…ď…ďe haa …ďe fooli on ; no O Ndaarndora on, O Senndindira hakkunde gom…óin…óo mu√Ī√Īii on e on lo'u…óo oo√Īii. Gom…óii Alla hoybina-nii on kon ko faggiti…óon e lunndagol yamiroore Nulaa…óo on. Alla ko Jom ∆Āural Mawngal e dow gom…óim…ďe …ďen ; tawde O Fewnirii…ďe gom…óinal, O Yaafiimo …ďe goopi ma…ď…ďe, O Ye…ói…ďe mbarjaari ti…ónaare ma…ď…ďe."
  3,153,"JaŇčtee onon muumini en, tuma nde dogayno…óon wo…ó…óitoo ka leydi √Īalnde uhud, …ďaawo nde waawa…óon sabu yeddugol Nulaa…óo on, gooto e mo'on alaano ndaarude oya. Nulaa…óo on no noddira on …ďaawo mon hakkunde sirkoo…ďe …ďen himo wi': "Aree e am jeyaa…ďe Alla, Aree e am". Alla Yo…ďitiri on e …óum …ďi…óteende sabu kon ko ballal ngal fuutori on e ko wareede Nulaa…óo on saakitii kon e mon. O Jippiniri …óum e mon fii wata on suno e ko ballal ngal fuuutorii on maa ko barme e maayireede he…ďi on …ďaawo nde anndu…óon Nulaa…óo on maayaali tawde …óum …ďu…ď…ďinno …ďer…óe mo'on. Alla no ko Humpitii…óo kala golle mo'on, hay huunde e fiyakuuji mo'on e golle mo'on suu…óaaki Mo."